snippet.title: MOJITO Woody's Rescue - Upcoming Indie 3d platformer developed with unreal engine
snippet.description:
Mojito Woody's Rescue is a cute 3D platformer adventure inspired by Super Mario 64/Odyssey.
Play as Mojito and find your best dog friend Woody, who disappeared with all his trophies when a suspicious storm hit their island

Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1664720/MOJITO_Woodys_Rescue/
